<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Maintainability</title>
    <para>
        <indexterm><primary>COFLoader</primary><secondary>maintainability</secondary></indexterm>
        The system should be maintainable by the internal software development team which has junior
        and intermediate level Java developers. To this end the architecture and design of the system should
        be documented suffciently for this team to be able to effectively maintain the system.
    </para>
